<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>My Website | Home</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0b1026;
    --text: #e9ecff;
    --accent: #61e1ff;
    --card: #151c41;
    --border: #2b2f5c;
  }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg), #1b2250);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  header {
    background: var(--card);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
  nav a {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-left: 16px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  nav a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    background: radial-gradient(800px at 50% 20%, rgba(97,225,255,0.15), transparent 70%);
  }
  .hero h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .hero p {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .btn {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #0b1026;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .btn:hover { filter: brightness(1.1); }
  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #b7bce6;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <h1>My Website</h1>
  <nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Play</a>
    <a href="#">About</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
  <h2>Welcome to My Website</h2>
  <p>Step into a creative space where ideas come alive. Explore projects, play interactive games, and discover new inspirations.</p>
  <button class="btn">Get Started</button>
</section>

<section class="features">
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Interactive Game</h3>
    <p>Play the Lucid Dream Runner and experience a surreal journey through dreamscapes.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>About Me</h3>
    <p>Learn more about the vision behind this site and the creative projects I’m building.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>Have ideas or feedback? Reach out and let’s collaborate on something amazing.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  © <span id="year"></span> My Website. All rights reserved.
</footer>

<script>
  document.getElementById("year").textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>
</body>
</html>
